data.description: Welcome to this charming, well-maintained home nestled in the heart of Clute!    This delightful property offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and contemporary living. With its prime location, this home provides easy access to local amenities, schools, and recreational facilities.    The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living area, dining space, and kitchen, making it ideal for both relaxing and entertaining.    The master suite provides a private retreat with its spacious layout, en-suite bathroom, and ample closet space. Kitchen is equipped with sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and opens up to the living room.    Outside, the property boasts a well-maintained yard that provides the perfect setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the fresh air.     Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home.
